Come on.
Give it everything you got.

34:59.880 --> 35:02.143
There it is.

35:02.187 --> 35:03.797
- [crying]

35:03.840 --> 35:06.147
That's good, right?

35:06.191 --> 35:09.019
Oh, my God.
Thank you both so much.

35:13.546 --> 35:15.548
[laughs]

35:18.768 --> 35:20.814
