36:29.187 --> 36:30.884
She never came in.

36:30.927 --> 36:32.190
- Oh.

36:32.233 --> 36:35.280
- Yeah, so maybe you can
track her down tomorrow.

36:35.323 --> 36:37.543
- Okay, I just,

36:37.586 --> 36:40.023
I really hope you don't
get into any trouble.

36:41.199 --> 36:43.157
- I wouldn't worry about that.

36:44.680 --> 36:46.247
- Thank you

36:46.291 --> 36:48.684
