38:12.115 --> 38:13.421
is driving me crazy.

38:13.465 --> 38:16.294
- No, Will and I
are not getting back together.

38:17.773 --> 38:19.297
- Okay, then what?

38:20.776 --> 38:22.735
I mean,
you been keeping secrets,

38:22.778 --> 38:25.128
shutting me out.
I mean, something's going on.

38:27.696 --> 38:29.089
- [sighs]

38:31.091 --> 38:33.223
- What?

38:34.224 --> 38:36.879
- I--I stole meds

38:36.923 --> 38:38.316
