38:40.405 --> 38:42.102
My mom was so sick,

38:42.145 --> 38:43.364
and nothing was working.

38:43.408 --> 38:45.323
I was desperate.
I wanted to tell you,

38:45.366 --> 38:49.283
but I felt so guilty
and so afraid.

38:49.327 --> 38:52.373
And now my mom
is dying in there,

38:52.417 --> 38:54.114
